items.name: Jakub Rozalski Style
items.description:
This is my attempt at recreating the painting style of Jakub Rozalski. This model works great at a strength 0.5-0.7 but if you plan to combine this lora with another style lora, then you should lower the strength down to 0.35-0.5. It also works best for landscape resolution.

If you wanna try the unique style i have been getting by using the Anato Finnstark lora together with this lora, then i recommend to have the Jakub Rozalski lora at strength 0.35 and the Anato Finnstark lora at 0.5-0.6

If you use higher strengths you will start to lose control over your prompts. I also strongly recommend to use these loras together:

LowRA

epi_noiseoffset

Add More Details

You should not use LowRA and epi_noiseoffset together since they both create a similar effect.

Also also try using the loras without much prompting. They usually default to a person standing in a field or just scenery images. Just keep your quality prompts and test it out. Works great with adding different color themes such as:

Yellow: (yellow theme)

Violet: (violet theme)

Green: (green theme)

Red: (red theme)

Blue: (blue theme)

Or try mixing two themes with:

[red theme:violet theme:0.5] this will generate a red theme the first 50% steps and then change over to a violet theme for the rest 50% steps.

items.name: Vex (Destiny franchise) LoRA
items.description:
WHAT IS THIS?

This is a LoRA based on Fluffusion / FluffyRock alpha (yiffymix) that generates vex from the video games Destiny and Destiny 2

Vex are evil humanoid robots with funky heads shaped like some animal features, canonically filled with "vex milk" hence the blue-white body, surrounded by a copper-ish armor.

Now, this lora generates not only all the kinds of vex in the game, but can also make new ones AND is unexpectedly good at mixing other species and characters to give them a robot/vex look and features!

HOW WAS THIS TRAINED?

Using kohya_ss, i made a first lora with all the images i could find online, then i prompted close to 500 images with it and selected ~100 of the best gens + the best quality original seeding images to make the second iteration of this lora, which is the one i'm sharing here. Spent ~10 hours on the whole process!

HOW TO PROMPT

Here's a list of specific prompts that are vital for using this lora.

You'll need AT LEAST ONE of these for it to work properly :

vexdestiny : the base term all images share, use if you don't care about the type of vex

vexgeneral : same as vexdestiny but only the gens that don't look like a specific type of vex, use if you want to get creative

vexgoblin : generates vex goblins (small vex with round-ish head)

vexhob : generates vex hobs (small-mid vex with two long "ears" on head)

vexminotaur : generates vex minotaurs (big and chubby vex with round head)

vexwyvern : generates vex wyverns (mid-big vex with large head)

vexatheon : experimental, supposed to generate the vex boss Atheon but is quite bad at it cuz not enough usable images exist, only way to get good results is to lower the weight of the lora to something like 0.5 or 0.6

Other notable prompts :

machine : important if you only want to generate actual vex and not furry hybrids, if you plan on mixing the vex armor/aesthetic with other species, leave "machine" out, leaving it out will have a furry bias.

red eyes : one of the main characteristic of the vex are their red eyes, use it and it'll strongly affect the prompt and get you a nice, big, glowing red eye. Can mess up furry hybrids so this is why it's not directly baked it.

For artstyle prompts, note that this lora was trained with pretty strong artstyle guidelines, to give great results without too much prompt customizatioon. HOWEVER artstyles can be applied to it but you'll have to lower the weight down a bit (more details below)

HOW TO WEIGHT THIS LORA

Anything between 0.5 and 1.0 will work well, tho i would suggest 0.6-0.8 since full weight has some defaults and is hard to change the artstyle. For furry hybrids, you can go as low as 0.3 (depends a lot on the species, some need higher values) and your characters will still have mostly vex robot parts and features.

Have fun!

LyCORIS/LoHA experiment trained 768x768 with tags, NR 64 + NA 32 dimensions.

Use Hires. fix (4x_RealisticRescaler, 4x-Ultrasharp upscalers with denoising strength around 0.3-0.6) for best details in txt2img!

For my notes on training and use of stable diffusion models, check https://sandner.art/articles/ai/

Support my work by buying me a coffee to keep those render cores go: https://ko-fi.com/airesearch

Have fun rendering!

items.description:
Hey

With this lora you'll be able to create several types of synths using these keywords. Some are followed by recommendations if you wish to get something closer to the original :

  • eurorack module

  • modular synth : add "cables, patch cables"

  • groovebox : add "colored touch pads, buttons"

  • volca

  • MS20 : add "keyboard"

  • TD-3 : silver, yellow and MO versions (you may have seen that i like acid)

  • TR-8O8 : add "colored buttons"

  • snth : a general keyword applied to all the dataset. Can be used for random results.

This Lora is captionned so try to always use these keywords in your prompts :

knobs, inputs, text, logos, LED indicators

Optional : keyboard, cables, patch cables, colored touch pads, buttons, small size, medium size, big size, wall size, (night, neon lights), man playing on a modular synth, studio, on table, multiple synths/modular synths

Lora weight : Anything works. I mostly used 0.8 or 1.

Enjoy and please share your results !! -

items.name: Cel-Shaded Art Style (LORA)
items.description:
Hey, everyone, I've decided to create a unique art style based off of different cel-shading styles (and other 2D mixed with 3D styles) like Telltale, Breath of the Wild, etc, and concocted a flat 2D design with 3D elements (like graphic novels, for instance).

v2 UPDATE:

(7/4/23): I fine-tuned and cleaned up the style on this fourth of July. Also, the recommended LoRA weight has been updated to being around 1-1.3 or so for full effect of the second version. Hope you enjoy!

Recommended settings:


LoRA weight: ~0.6-1 (for v1.0)

If you're doing hires. fix, I suggest the denoising range of ~0.55-0.7

CFG scale: 5-7

Checkpoints: I recommend Deliberate since it's the one that I tested out the most, and provided accurate results (but you can experiment with others as well)

Samplers: Euler a, DPM++ 2M Karras, or DPM++ SDE Karras

Negative prompt that works well:

paintings, sketches, (worst quality:2), (low quality:2), (normal quality:2), dot, mole, lowers, normal quality, monochrome, grayscale, lowers, text, error, cropped, worst quality, low quality, jpeg artifacts, ugly, duplicate, morbid, mutilated, out of frame, extra fingers, mutated hands, poorly drawn hands, poorly drawn face, mutation, deformed, blurry, dehydrated, bad anatomy, bad proportions, extra limbs, cloned face, disfigured, gross proportions, malformed limbs, missing arms, missing legs, extra arms, extra legs, fused fingers, too many fingers, long neck, username, watermark, signature, less than five fingers, EasyNegative, ng_deepnegative_v1_75t

Suggestions and feedback are always welcome!

I hope you enjoy my LoRA!

foreword（基本介绍）

It is a Chinese ink style Lora model

  • Best practice: arbitrary resolution, better Lora weight 0.5-1, clip=2, sampler DMP ++2M karras, 20-40step, using Chinese ink painting to call lora, more parameters can refer to my sketch

这是一个中国水墨风格的lora模型

  • 最佳实践：分辨率随意，Lora权重0.5-1更好，clip=2，采样器DMP ++2M karras，20-40step，使用Chinese ink painting调用lora，更多参数可以参考我的示意图

CONCEPT（概念）

可以搭配任意大模型使用，这个版本更适合远景，全身，当然看你喜好，目前测试如果你想只想要一点点的效果但想要有影响物体我建议Lora值是0.2-0.4这样也许会有一点效果，但不至于太强烈，目前还处于基础版本，后续可能会更多的迭代与更新Lora

我是基于anything大模型训练的lora，因此我认为他的适配强度很高目前我在测试Lora适配模型的契合程度


Can be used with any large model, this version is more suitable for the vision, the whole body, of course, depending on your preferences, the current test if you want to only want a little effect but want to have an impact object I suggest that the Lora value is 0.2-0.4 so that may have a little effect, but not too strong, is still in the basic version, the follow-up may be more iterations and updates Lora

I trained lora based on anything large model, so I think its fit strength is very high and I am currently testing the fit degree of Lora fit model

items.name: Boris Groh
items.description:
Warning: contains both safe and unsafe content.

This model was trained by me in Dreambooth on 49 paintings and then merged with the text encoders of 2 other models.

Boris Groh is a digital artist. Most of his works depict gloomy residential areas populated by strange creatures. One of the main themes of Groh’s paintings is a giant skeleton wandering in the everyday environment of urban life, showing curiosity, sadness and loneliness. Write simple prompts (due to the small dataset) and don’t forget about the trigger “art by Boris Groh”.

Contains noise offset.

警告：包含安全和不安全的内容。

这个模型是我在 Dreambooth 上用 49 幅画训练的，然后与另外 2 个模型的文本编码器合并的。

Boris Groh 是一位数字艺术家。他的大部分作品描绘了充满奇怪生物的阴暗住宅区。Groh 的画作的一个主要主题是一个巨大的骷髅，在城市生活的日常环境中游荡，表现出好奇、悲伤和孤独。写一些简单的提示（因为数据集很小），并且不要忘记触发器 “art by Boris Groh”。

包含 noise offset。

Предупреждение: включает как безопасное, так и небезопасное содержимое.

Борис Грох — цифровой художник. Большинство его работ изображают мрачные спальные районы, населённые странными существами. Одна из основных тем картин Гроха — это гигантский скелет, блуждающий в повседневном окружении городской жизни, проявляя любопытство, печаль и одиночество. items.name: LEOSAM's 中国门神画风格 Chinese Traditional Door Gods Painting Style LoRA
items.description:
🤝如您有模型定制或其他合作、咨询需求，请联系Wechat: 13439222668。请简单注明来意，时间有限不闲聊哈，谢谢理解！

If you have any model customization or other collaboration and consultation needs, please contact Wechat: 13439222668. Kindly provide a brief description of your inquiry, as there's limited time and no time for casual chats. Thank you!

Traditional Chinese Door Gods, rooted in ancient folk beliefs, represent a form of folk art that wards off evil spirits and prays for peace. Door God paintings, as a type of folk painting, experienced rapid development since the Tang Dynasty and have a history of more than a thousand years. Traditional Chinese Door God paintings often portray valiant generals, such as Qin Qiong and Yuchi Gong, who are endowed with divine powers to protect families and repel evil. The artistic style of Door God paintings is unique, characterized by bold lines, rich colors, and vivid imagery. Common elements in traditional Chinese Door God paintings include fierce tigers, auspicious dragons, and weapons, symbolizing family harmony and career success. During important festivals like the Spring Festival, every household would paste Door God paintings on their doors to pray for peace and ward off evil spirits.

This Lora model was trained using 23 pairs, totaling 46 traditional Chinese Door God paintings. The mandatory Trigger Word for using this Lora model is "chinese door gods". You may use this Trigger Word alone when you simply want to reference the Door God painting style. However, if you wish to closely replicate the appearance and composition of Door God paintings, in addition to "chinese door gods," you should include phrases like "a painting of"/"a drawing of..." and "White background" in your prompt. Furthermore, you can specify the orientation of the Door God character by adding the keywords "zuobian" (left-facing) or "youbian" (right-facing).

This Lora model has been tested and found to be compatible with 2D, 2.5D, and 3D large-scale models. When used with 3D photorealistic models, some fascinating visuals emerge, as demonstrated in the example images. Feel free to unleash your imagination and create imaginative, personalized Door God paintings!

中国传统门神，源于古代民间信仰，是一种具有辟邪镇煞、祈求平安的民间艺术形式。门神画作为一种民间绘画，自唐代起快速发展，至今已有超千年历史。中国传统门神画多以勇猛的武将形象为题材，如秦琼、尉迟恭等，这些英勇的武将被赋予保护家庭、驱邪避凶的神力。门神画的画风独具特色，以其厚重的线条、浓烈的色彩、生动的形象脱颖而出。中国传统门神画中常见的元素有猛虎、祥龙、刀枪等，寓意家庭安宁、事业成功。在春节等重要节日，家家户户都会在门口贴上门神画以祈求家宅安康，驱邪避邪。

本Lora模型使用了23对共46张中国传统门神画训练而成。本lora模型使用时必须调用的Trigger Word为chinese door gods。当您只是想借鉴门神画画风时，使用这一个Trigger Word就好。但如果您希望高度还原门神画的造型与布局，那么除了chinese door gods以外，您需要在提示词中使用a painting of/ a drawing of...，White background。另外您可以通过添加zuobian或youbian这两个关键词，设定你所画的门神角色是面向左侧还是面向右侧。

经过测试，对于2D、2.5D以及3D大模型，本Lora模型均可以很好兼容。在使用3D写实类模型时，会出现一些非常有趣的画面，比如我在示意图中所演示的。总之欢迎大家充分发挥想象力，创作出天马行空的个性化门神画作！
